These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-1::.
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: rugby, swimming, cycling, baseball, basketball, climbing, water-polo
The people have 7 different hobbies: photography, rock-climbing, drawing, singing, puzzles, collecting, writing
 1. the person who's sport is cycling is on the far left##1
 2. the person who's sport is baseball is not the person who's hobby is collecting##6
 3. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 4. the person who's hobby is writing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##5
 5. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left or right of the person who's sport is water-polo##3
 6. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
 7. the person who's sport is climbing is somewhere between the person who's sport is swimming and the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##7
 8. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
 9. the person who's hobby is singing is somewhere between the person who's sport is basketball and the person who's hobby is drawing##7
10. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is photography##3
11. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the far left##1
12. the person who's sport is baseball is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is writing##5
13. the person who's sport is baseball is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is climbing##5
14. the person who's sport is water-polo is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is basketball##5
15. the person who's sport is basketball is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4     |     5     |     6     |    7    |
| Sport          | cycling    | rugby    | swimming | climbing | baseball | basketball    | water-polo |
| Hobby   | puzzles | photography | drawing  | collecting   | singing    | rock-climbing | writing |

