.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-2::.
There are 7 different favourite colors: aquamarine, blue, coral, yellow, brown, light-blue, ivory
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: family, spy, superhero, western, scientific, martial-arts, musical
 1. the person watching martial-arts movies is somewhere between the person who likes ivory and the person who likes blue##7
 2. the person watching musical movies is the person who likes yellow##1
 3. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1
 4. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the person who likes light-blue##1
 5. the person who likes aquamarine is somewhere between the person watching western movies and the person watching spy movies##7
 6. the person who likes light-blue is somewhere between the person who likes yellow and the person watching superhero movies##7
 7. the person who likes brown is somewhere between the person who likes yellow and the person who likes blue##7
 8. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
 9. the person watching scientific movies is somewhere to the left of the person who likes brown##5
10. the person who likes brown is somewhere to the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##5
11. the person watching martial-arts movies is not the person who likes ivory##6
12. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
13. the person watching scientific movies is between the person watching western movies and the person who likes yellow##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |       5       |      6      |    7    |
| Color    | ivory  | coral | light-blue | yellow | aquamarine     | brown | blue  |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | martial-arts | spy  | musical  | scientific | western      | family |

