.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-4::.
7 different pets are kept: pony, frog, rabbit, appleing, rat, bird, goldfish
There 7 different types of food: avocado, spinach, artichoke, apple, onion, banana, peach
 1. the person eating peach is somewhere to the right of the person eating spinach##5
 2. the owner of the rabbit is in an odd position##4
 3. the owner of the rat is somewhere to the left of the person eating peach##5
 4. the owner of the rat is somewhere to the right of the person eating banana##5
 5. the owner of the appleing is somewhere to the left of the owner of the goldfish##5
 6. the person eating banana is on the right of the person eating spinach##1
 7. the person eating artichoke is somewhere between the person eating spinach and the person eating onion##7
 8. the owner of the appleing is on the far left##1
 9. the person eating onion is somewhere to the left of the owner of the pony##5
10. the owner of the bird is in an even position##4
11. the owner of the bird is somewhere between the owner of the rat and the owner of the frog##7
12. the person eating apple is somewhere to the right of the owner of the goldfish##5
13. the person eating apple is on the left of the person eating avocado##1
14. the owner of the rabbit is somewhere to the left of the person eating peach##5
15. the owner of the goldfish is on the left or right of the person eating apple##3
16. the person eating onion is somewhere to the left of the person eating artichoke##5
17. the person eating apple is between the owner of the bird and the person eating banana##2
18. the owner of the rat is not the person eating peach##6
19. the person eating avocado is somewhere to the right of the person eating spinach##5

.:: Answer ::.
