 3. the person playing whist is on the far left##1
 4. the person driving the van is not the person playing whist##6
 5. the person driving the van is somewhere to the left of the person driving the helicopter##5
 6. the person playing mah-jongg is somewhere to the left of the person playing go##5
 7. the person playing go is somewhere to the left of the person playing poker##5
 8. the person driving the helicopter is somewhere to the left of the person driving the ship##5
 9. the person driving the airplane is not the person playing go##6
10. the person playing mah-jongg is somewhere to the left of the person driving the van##5
11. the person playing go is somewhere to the left of the person playing canasta##5
12. the person playing poker is the person driving the car##1
13. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person playing whist##1
14. the person playing mah-jongg is the person driving the subway##1
15. the person playing poker is on the left of the person playing chess##1
16. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1

