 5. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in july is somewhere between the person drinking soy-milk and the person drinking almond-milk##7
 7. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
 8. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in november##3
 9. the person drinking soy-milk is not the person who's birthday is in september##6
10. the person drinking lemonade is in an even position##4
