 3. the person playing chess is on the left or right of the bongani-smoker##3
 4. the person playing mah-jongg is on the far left or far right##3
 5. the person playing bridge is somewhere to the left of the bolivar-smoker##5
 6. the game-smoker is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
 7. the game-smoker is on the right of the bongani-smoker##1
